[name]
Non-quoting guesswork disabled

[options]
guesswork none

[input]
=head1 GUESSWORK

Both hyphens-in-compound-words and e-mail should be escaped.

Function: foo(), bar::baz(), _private::_stuff()

Manpage: foo(1), Pod::Man(3perl), git-rebase(1)

Variables: $foo, @bar::baz, %Pod::Blah

[output]
.SH GUESSWORK
.IX Header "GUESSWORK"
Both hyphens\-in\-compound\-words and e\-mail should be escaped.
.PP
Function: foo(), bar::baz(), _private::_stuff()
.PP
Manpage: foo(1), Pod::Man(3perl), git\-rebase(1)
.PP
Variables: $foo, @bar::baz, %Pod::Blah
